reviewText: This is an excellent tool for the home owner who want to change their old cabinets and don't have or want to spend the money to replace them.  The instructions are very easy to follow, no complex steps to follow.  I picked up my products that the local Home Depot store (water based paint, gripper primer, behr faux glaze, some lint free rags, and brushes).  This video is short and too the point.  He walks you through the whole process.  It was definitely worth the money.
